Give our customer service team a call at (877) 839-3330 for help with a quote or order. Move your equipment and supplies in style in Sandusky Lee's Elite Transport Double-Door Mobile Storage Cabinet. This 22-gauge steel mobile cabinet has adjustable shelves and a fixed bottom shelf; each supports up to 200 pounds of evenly distributed weight. The recessed lock ensures that your items stay protected from theft and vandalism. Casters are positioned for great support and so that the cabinet can be placed flush to the wall. The powder-coat paint finish resists scratches and comes in several great colors. Sandusky Lee's Elite Transport Series Double-Door Storage Cabinet ships completely assembled except for the casters and optional side handle and comes backed by a five-year warranty. $384.95 - $569.95
